JFalalalala, lalalalad

753
00:34:23,061 --> 00:34:25,689
♪ 'Tis the season to be jolly ♪

754
00:34:25,730 --> 00:34:29,428
JFalalalala, lalalalad

755
00:34:29,467 --> 00:34:31,526
♪ Don we now our gay apparel ♪

756
00:34:31,570 --> 00:34:33,834
JFalalalala, lalalalad

757
00:34:34,072 --> 00:34:37,508
I Troll the ancient
Yuletide carol I

758
00:34:37,542 --> 00:34:40,807
JFalalalala, lalalalad

759
00:34:40,845 --> 00:34:43,576
(all laughing)

760
00:34:55,527 --> 00:34:58,121
(sighing)

761
00:35:07,172 --> 00:35:08,139
Everything okay?

762
00:35:08,173 --> 00:35:09,607
I'm just frustrated.

763
00:35:09,641 --> 00:35:11,336
I thought, once I got here,

764
00:35:11,376 --> 00:35:13,435
a solution for the ranch
would just come to me.

765
00:35:13,478 --> 00:35:14,775
It usually does.

766
00:35:14,813 --> 00:35:17,373
Well, your first problem is

767
00:35:17,415 --> 00:35:18,678
is there's nothing's
quick Big Fork.

768
00:35:20,418 --> 00:35:22,580
And the second is
you should be at the ranch

769
00:35:22,621 --> 00:35:24,783
for your inspiration, not here.

770
00:35:24,823 --> 00:35:27,224
Now, go, get some sleep.

771
00:35:27,258 --> 00:35:29,693
I'll drive you out
in the morning.

772
00:35:29,728 --> 00:35:32,527
That's so nice.
Thank you.

773
00:35:32,564 --> 00:35:33,861
Think nothing of it.

774
00:35:42,307 --> 00:35:44,867
- Pops: Hey!
- Sara: Hil

775
00:35:44,909 --> 00:35:46,673
Hello! Good morning!

776
00:35:46,711 --> 00:35:48,509
Hey, Pops.

777
00:35:48,546 --> 00:35:50,708
So, how are you
fixed for egg nog?

778
00:35:50,749 --> 00:35:52,581
Running a little low.

779
00:35:52,617 --> 00:35:56,679
Any chance you could find some
time to whip up another batch?

780
00:35:56,721 --> 00:35:58,689
Kay:
Well, I can make time.

