01:11:35,057 --> 01:11:36,650
Did you want to
go for a stroll?

1483
01:11:36,692 --> 01:11:38,717
I'd love to.

1484
01:11:38,761 --> 01:11:41,890
Okay. You know that "stroll"
means "walking slowly," right?

1485
01:11:41,931 --> 01:11:43,626
I'll do my best.

1486
01:11:43,666 --> 01:11:47,569
Okay.

1487
01:11:47,603 --> 01:11:49,594
I think this is the first time

1488
01:11:49,639 --> 01:11:51,073
we've ever walked
at the same pace.

1489
01:11:51,307 --> 01:11:53,332
Yeah. Congratulations.

1490
01:11:53,376 --> 01:11:55,743
I think you're
finally on Montana Time.

1491
01:11:58,815 --> 01:12:01,045
Have I thanked you already
for saving our ranch?

1492
01:12:01,083 --> 01:12:03,848
Yes,
numerous times.

1493
01:12:03,886 --> 01:12:05,479
Good.

1494
01:12:08,591 --> 01:12:10,992
Have I thanked you for
reminding me

1495
01:12:11,027 --> 01:12:13,860
what it feels like...

1496
01:12:13,896 --> 01:12:16,593
to fall head over heels
for someone?

1497
01:12:16,632 --> 01:12:18,566
No.

1498
01:12:21,737 --> 01:12:24,104
(sighing)

1499
01:12:24,340 --> 01:12:27,105
I feel the same way.

1500
01:12:31,047 --> 01:12:33,914
But?

1501
01:12:33,950 --> 01:12:37,944
Maybe that's
why we shouldn't stay.

1502
01:12:37,987 --> 01:12:40,684
Why not?

1503
01:12:40,723 --> 01:12:43,818
I mean, we have to leave
right after Christmas.

1504
01:12:43,860 --> 01:12:46,454
And...
and then what happens?

1505
01:12:46,495 --> 01:12:48,589
How does this work?

1506
01:12:48,631 --> 01:12:50,690
I don't know.

1507
01:12:50,733 --> 01:12:54,067
I don't,
but we'll figure it out.

1508
01:12:54,103 --> 01:12:55,434
No, Travis.

1509
01:12:55,471 --> 01:12:57,803
This is your life.
This is your home.

1510
01:12:57,840 --> 01:13:01,140
I have a daughter at
school in Los Angles.

1511
01:13:01,377 --> 01:13:04,472
I have a job. I have security.
I cannot give that up.

1512
01:13:04,513 --> 01:13:06,003
I'm sorry.

1513
01:13:09,952 --> 01:13:12,114
I understand.

1514
01:13:17,827 --> 01:13:19,693
I better get back to Chloe.

1515
01:13:35,912 --> 01:13:38,643
I don't want to leave.

1516
01:13:38,681 --> 01:13:40,115
We should be going to
Christmas Eve dinner tonight,

1517
01:13:40,149 --> 01:13:41,639
not the airport.

1518
01:13:41,684 --> 01:13:43,880
Chloe, I know you're upset,
but if we stayed,

1519
01:13:43,920 --> 01:13:45,513
it would just make
things harder.

