I was protecting you.

1530
01:14:21,123 --> 01:14:23,820
I was just trying to
keep you from any more pain.

1531
01:14:25,461 --> 01:14:27,555
I was doing the same thing.

1532
01:14:30,166 --> 01:14:32,635
That's the best thing
aboutthis place, wasn't it?

1533
01:14:32,668 --> 01:14:36,935
People slow down,
they talk, they share.

1534
01:14:36,973 --> 01:14:39,635
Like right now.

1535
01:14:39,675 --> 01:14:41,803
Just like right now.

1536
01:14:44,146 --> 01:14:45,978
I still miss Dad.

1537
01:14:46,015 --> 01:14:47,540
I know.

1538
01:14:47,583 --> 01:14:49,847
Sodol.

1539
01:14:49,885 --> 01:14:52,855
I have something for you.

1540
01:14:52,888 --> 01:14:54,481
I was going to wait
until Christmas,

1541
01:14:54,523 --> 01:14:56,855
but I want you to have it now.

1542
01:15:00,196 --> 01:15:02,062
It's for the
Christmas charm bracelet

1543
01:15:02,098 --> 01:15:03,793
Daddy gave you when
you were little.

1544
01:15:03,833 --> 01:15:05,733
